{"word":"δέμνιον","slug":"δέμνιον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δέμνιον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δέμω'><el>δέμω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>δέμνια</el>, <i>the bedstead</i> or <i>matrass</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>a bed, bedding</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}